||[[span class="fixed"]][[# git-branch]][http://schacon.github.com/git/git-branch.html branch] [-r|-a] _
[http://schacon.github.com/git/git-branch.html branch] [@@--@@contains|@@--@@merged] [#COMMIT COMMIT] _
