 _
##gray|//none//## _
 _
Create a bookmark for the parent changeset of the working directory or REV. _
 _
##gray|//Mercurial does not have tracking bookmarks.//## _
 _
Rename bookmark NAME1 to NAME2. _
 _
Delete the bookmark NAME.||
